Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,, largely: adv. 在很大程度上\N Lesson 29. Funny or not? Whether we find a joke funny or not largely depends on where we have been brought up.\N第29课。有趣与否？我们是否发现一个笑话很有趣，这在很大程度上取决于我们的何处。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,, The sense of humor is mysteriously bound up with national characteristics.\N幽默感与民族特征有关。
