Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:01:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,, It is called, Sick Humor. Comedians base their jokes on tragic situation like violent death or serious accidents.\N这被称为病幽默。喜剧演员开玩笑的基础是诸如暴力死亡或严重事故的悲惨局势。
