Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,, You to judge for yourself. A man who had broken his right leg was taken to hospital a few weeks before Christmas.\N您要自己判断。一个摔断右腿的男人被送往圣诞节前几周。
