Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,, dread: v.   惧怕, recovery: n.   康复\N He dreaded having to spend Christmas in hospital. Though the doctors did his best, the patient's recovery was slow.\N他害怕必须在医院度过圣诞节。尽管医生尽力而为，但患者的康复速度很慢。
